Sentencas: A micro tubular solid oxide fuel cells (MT-SOFCs) with a cell configuration of Ni impregnated Ni -Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 (GDC)/GDC/La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (LSCF)-GDC has been prepared by the phase inversion and impregnation technique.
Titulo: Effect of nickel impregnated hollow fiber anode for micro tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A special asymmetrical structure consisting of a sponge-like layer and a finger-like porous layer for hollow fiber anode is obtained by the phase inversion.
Titulo: Effect of nickel impregnated hollow fiber anode for micro tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Fine Ni specie particles are then coated on the surface of anode using impregnation method.
Titulo: Effect of nickel impregnated hollow fiber anode for micro tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The enhancement in electronic conductivity of anode by Ni modification is beneficial to current collection of MT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Effect of nickel impregnated hollow fiber anode for micro tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Meanwhile, the catalytic activity of anode is also improved due to the introduction of Ni nano-particles.
Titulo: Effect of nickel impregnated hollow fiber anode for micro tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Thus, the Ni modified MT-SOFCs exhibit high power densities, such as 0.69 W cm(-2) at 600 degrees C.
Titulo: Effect of nickel impregnated hollow fiber anode for micro tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The encouraging results demonstrate that the Ni impregnation is an effective way to improve anode microstructure of MT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Effect of nickel impregnated hollow fiber anode for micro tubular solid oxide fuel cells
